&lt;p&gt;快来听小岳岳的相声专场吧！机不可失，失不再来！&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.8666666666666667&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/RiacFDBX14xBJkCOJ3ibPn34UgPePZjYvsuAGsKcszoia8iagWZ4fwvjAxNsRMGOEz0dBicqPaPRicXka1ic6BmvjM6lA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;360&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;你最想在北美听谁的演唱会？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;快来投票并在评论区留言吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;评论越多，偶像来北美的几率就越大哦！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;马上点击原文链接抢购小岳岳专场门票吧！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;162&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCqO0ZUuzg71XoT0ibhqSSWSBRgg0zNKjhEgo7SrfN0M3JRgNSH16KCxWD0ibib6evFwiaMgxQNqLSRUA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3083067092651757&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCqO0ZUuzg71XoT0ibhqSSWSBRgg0zNKjhEgo7SrfN0M3JRgNSH16KCxWD0ibib6evFwiaMgxQNqLSRUA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;626&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;714&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xAmZl0ClGXuWms73DIMtjkED21UddIoyC5g74dibrLFPzX35NNQshseqEkzZ0ST1mRnJoG1Wc09ZcQ/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.3574660633484164&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xAmZl0ClGXuWms73DIMtjkED21UddIoyC5g74dibrLFPzX35NNQshseqEkzZ0ST1mRnJoG1Wc09ZcQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;663&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
